OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fthickening through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. Winds also strengthening,
OL,8,Fwith upland gales likely, and perhaps
OL,9,Fsome rain for a time across the
OL,10,FDerbyshire hills. Likely staying frost
OL,11,Ffree.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA cloudy but largely dry
OL,14,Fstart. Some outbreaks of rain possible
OL,15,Fby midday, before occasionally heavy
OL,16,Fand blustery rain moves southeast late
OL,17,Fafternoon, likely reaching northern
OL,18,Fparts before dusk. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
